info:
(1) Responsibilities:

1．Keep learning relevant skills on the job,improving personal understanding of foreign trade;

2．Familiar with foreign trade business process,provide necessary business support for the business team through the execution of inquiry, order placing and tracking and customers development;

3．Analyze the market trends and evaluate the demand,collect customers information;

4．Coordinate the work arrangement of the department,complete various tasks assigned by the leader;

5．Able to grow rapidly during the internship;

6．At least 3 working days per week.

(2)Qualifications:

1.Target Population:
1)Chinese students who graduated from December 2025 to June 2026 (bachelor's or master's degree from overseas universities)
2)Foreign students to China (above the first year of university)
3)Major in International trade, International Business, Marketing, Business English, etc;

2．Fluent in written and oral English.Knowledge of Spanish, French or German is a plus;

3．Familiar with office software including excel,word,Power point and others;

4．Good at communication,able to work under pressure,strong sense of responsibility and teamwork.
